<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="title">配送调度台</view>
    <view class="subtitle">这里集中查看用户订单，配送端手动选择 AprilTag 0 或 1 后，再开始配送。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="service-banner status-{{serviceState}}">
    {{serviceMessage}}
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">调度操作</view>
    <view class="section-caption">当前调度台只保留 AprilTag 选择。进入订单详情后，由配送端手动选择 0 或 1。</view>
    <view class="button-row">
      <button class="primary-btn" loading="{{loading}}" bindtap="fetchOrders">刷新订单</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">待调度订单</view>
    <view class="section-caption">新提交的订单会先出现在这里，进入详情后手动选择 AprilTag。</view>
    <block wx:if="{{loadError}}">
      <view class="empty">{{loadError}}</view>
    </block>
    <block wx:elif="{{loading && !pendingOrders.length && !activeOrders.length}}">
      <view class="empty">正在加载订单列表...</view>
    </block>
    <block wx:elif="{{pendingOrders.length}}">
      <block wx:for="{{pendingOrders}}" wx:key="order_id">
        <view class="list-item" data-order-id="{{item.order_id}}" bindtap="openDetail">
          <view class="item-title">{{item.order_id}}</view>
          <view class="item-subtitle">用户：{{item.receiver_id}} | AprilTag号：{{item.apriltag_text}}</view>
          <view class="status-badge status-{{item.status}}">{{item.status_text}}</view>
        </view>
      </block>
    </block>
    <view wx:else class="empty">当前没有待处理订单。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">执行中订单</view>
    <view class="section-caption">已分配或正在配送中的订单会在这里持续更新状态。</view>
    <block wx:if="{{loadError}}">
      <view class="empty">{{loadError}}</view>
    </block>
    <block wx:elif="{{activeOrders.length}}">
      <block wx:for="{{activeOrders}}" wx:key="order_id">
        <view class="list-item" data-order-id="{{item.order_id}}" bindtap="openDetail">
          <view class="item-title">{{item.order_id}}</view>
          <view class="item-subtitle">用户：{{item.receiver_id}} | AprilTag号：{{item.apriltag_text}}</view>
          <view class="status-badge status-{{item.status}}">{{item.status_text}}</view>
        </view>
      </block>
    </block>
    <view wx:else class="empty">当前没有执行中的订单。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="page-footnote">
    <view>第九届（2026）全国大学生嵌入式芯片与系统设计竞赛</view>
    <view class="page-footnote-team">地线引力队</view>
  </view>
</view>
